    "statement": {
      "informal": "The base F-family operator S_F1(x,y) = exp(x) - log(y), restated for the subtraction test, is not pointwise equal to subtraction. Witness: at (1,1), S_F1 evaluates to exp(1) which is greater than 0 = 1−1.",
